            "title": "Notorial vol.3|微积分第一集：极限",
            "date_published": "2024-03-25T12:24:09.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"sth-2-say\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#sth-2-say\">#</a> sth 2 say</h1>\n<div class=\"note info\">\n<p>本站现在（学期里）没活了，只能更点学习资料了。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>虽然猫娘挺可爱，但微积分却是真实存在的。 ——（估计是）牛顿</p>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"函数的极限\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#函数的极限\">#</a> 函数的极限</h1>\n<h2 id=\"有限点处的极限\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#有限点处的极限\">#</a> 有限点处的极限</h2>\n<p>有一个函数，如果在自变量 x 无限接近某个确定的值 x0 时（记为 x→x0，x≠x0），函数值 f (x) 无限趋近于确定的常数 A，就可以说</p>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></math>\n</p>\n<p>幂函数、指数函数、对数函数等初级基本函数在定义域内每一点处的极限相当于此处的函数值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"无限大处的极限\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#无限大处的极限\">#</a> 无限大处的极限</h2>\n<p>有一个函数，如果在自变量 x 无限增大时（记为 x→x0，x≠x0），函数值 f (x) 无限趋近于确定的常数 A，就可以说<br />\n \n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi></mrow></munder><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></math>\n</p>\n<h1 id=\"函数极限的运算法则\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#函数极限的运算法则\">#</a> 函数极限的运算法则</h1>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">[</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo>±</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo>±</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></math>\n</p>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">[</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></math>\n</p>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mi>g</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac></math>\n</p>\n<div class=\"note info\">\n<p>暂时跳过示例</p>\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"无穷小\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#无穷小\">#</a> 无穷小</h1>\n<h2 id=\"定义\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#定义\">#</a> 定义</h2>\n<p>当 x→x0 时或 x→∞ 时，f (x) → 0，则这时 f (x) 叫做  x→x0 时的无穷小。即</p>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mi>f</mi><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"INNER\"><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OPEN\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"CLOSE\">) = 0</mo></mrow></math>\n<br />\n 时的函数值</p>\n<h2 id=\"无穷小的比较\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#无穷小的比较\">#</a> 无穷小的比较</h2>\n<p>如果 <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mi>α</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mi>β</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math> </p>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>若</mo><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mfrac><mi>β</mi><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>，那么</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>是比</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>高阶的无穷小</mo></math>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>若</mo><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mfrac><mi>β</mi><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi><mo>，那么</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>是比</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>高阶的无穷小</mo></math>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>若</mo><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mfrac><mi>β</mi><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>，那么</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>是比</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>同阶的无穷小</mo></math>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>若</mo><munder><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></munder><mfrac><mi>β</mi><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>，那么</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>是比</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>等阶的无穷小，记为</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>∼</mo><mi>β</mi></math>\n</p>\n<p>常用的近似：<br />\n\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>当</mo><mi>x</mi><mo accent=\"false\" stretchy=\"false\">→</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>时</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∼</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"NONE\">⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∼</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"NONE\">⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>sin</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"NONE\">⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"NONE\">⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></math>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"等阶无穷小的变换\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#等阶无穷小的变换\">#</a> 等阶无穷小的变换</h2>\n<p>\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><mo>如果</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>α</mi><mrow><msup><mi></mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mi>β</mi><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>β</mi><mrow><msup><mi></mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mo>,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∃</mi><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>β</mi><mrow><msup><mi></mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mi>β</mi></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>则</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mfrac><mi>β</mi><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo data-mjx-texclass=\"OP\" movablelimits=\"true\">lim</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>β</mi><mrow><msup><mi></mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mrow><msup><mi>α</mi><mrow></mrow></msup><mrow><msup><mi></mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow></mrow></mfrac></math>\n</p>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/spoiler.css\" type=\"text/css\"><script src=\"/js/spoiler.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" async></script>",
